Cook pasta according to package directions. Rinse with cool water and drain. Combine Hidden Valley(R) Original Ranch Salad(R) Dressing & Seasoning Mix with milk and mayonnaise in a bowl, creating 1 cup dressing. In a small bowl, whisk the dressing together with the oil until emulsified. In a large bowl, add the pasta and the remaining ingredients. Add the dressing and toss until well coated. Chill covered for 1 hour before serving.